{"tid":982424,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有片慎入【鱷魚殺科學家】實驗池鱷魚躍起8呎 強拉人落水活活咬死","createTime":"2019-01-15T06:20:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-15T13:23:20.000Z","uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d1502b6967502537dd8ce653578f8eca0c369801","tid":982424,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T06:20:13.000Z","msg":"印尼一名女科學家上周五被鱷魚咬死。44歲的圖沃（Deasy Tuwo）在北蘇拉威西省的研究中心扔肉進鱷魚池餵「Merry」時，被牠拖進區內咬死。被發現時「Merry」仍叼着圖沃的屍體。<br />\n<br />\n圖沃的同事魯門根（Erling Rumengan）表示，在池中見到「異物」浮面，看真才知是圖沃。當時不敢觸碰她的屍體，所以報警。他懷疑「Merry」已經吃飽，才沒把圖沃整個吃掉。<br />\n<br />\n由於「Merry」一見人想取走圖沃屍體就表現兇惡，救援人員幾經辛苦才撈回屍體。官員相信，「Merry」站了起來，跳起將池邊2.4米(8呎)高牆後的圖沃拖進池中。<br />\n<br />\n朋友形容死者圖沃為人文靜，熱愛動物。至於身長5.2米的「Merry」，過往有襲擊其他鱷魚的紀錄，但沒想過牠會襲擊人。工作人員其後綁起「Merry」運走，檢查牠胃中是否殘留圖沃的身體部份。<br />\n<br />\n警方正欲聯絡研究中心的東主，相信是日本商人，事發時不在中心內。警方正調查他是否取得許可，飼養鱷魚及其他珍貴的水生動物。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4eb28S2EjLQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4eb28S2EjLQ&d=IaM7PEbqaTm0p1rdo6owMZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=7fce194e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4eb28S2EjLQ</a>"},{"pid":"27cab097953691b1ba155d2a66c1e693cb1df1e8","tid":982424,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T06:22:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52377b3fb08bc68d6b451e58687e66204b435b32","tid":982424,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T09:54:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cecd7751f65cc8b2f7d91446ae2349d7ebf7eb6","tid":982424,"uid":139322,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-15T10:04:55.000Z","msg":"樓主好慘 無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d0ebe3a9388a6876446316786e2fa059b952baa","tid":982424,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime"